- Look!

16:03.563 --> 16:07.465
[Cubby] The statues head
is hollow like a cave!

16:07.467 --> 16:11.469
Good eye, Cubby.
Bucky, head inside that head!

16:16.141 --> 16:19.110
[all growling]

16:19.112 --> 16:21.212
[Jake whispering]
Yo-ho. We did it!

16:21.214 --> 16:25.183
We lost the shark!
And we got two gold doubloons.

16:25.185 --> 16:27.652
Let's grab them and go deeper.

16:31.190 --> 16:34.659
I want whatever treasure
those popinjays are after.

16:34.661 --> 16:39.597
Um, cap'n? You might
want to look over that-a way.

16:39.599 --> 16:42.166
Sloshing chum buckets!

16:42.168 --> 16:45.203
Keep pumping, Bones!
The cap'n and Mr. Smee

16:45.205 --> 16:48.272
need plenty of air to breathe
down below them waves.

16:48.274 --> 16:51.242
[Hook and Smee screaming]

16:51.244 --> 16:54.746
You silly gooses!
There's no shark up there!

16:57.182 --> 17:00.551
That hand normally holds a
giant shell and the pink pearl!

17:00.553 --> 17:03.721
- They're missing!
- Where do you think they went?

17:03.723 --> 17:06.157
Maybe it fell
to the sea floor.

17:06.159 --> 17:07.225
Good thinking, Izzy!

17:11.230 --> 17:15.600
[Skully] Crackers!
That is one giant clam shell.

17:15.602 --> 17:17.702
It's the shell from
Neptune's hand!

17:17.704 --> 17:19.303
Something knocked it off.

17:19.305 --> 17:23.274
It must have drifted down
and landed here.

17:23.276 --> 17:27.278
Look! A pale pink glow
coming from beneath the shell.

17:27.280 --> 17:29.580
The pink pearl must be
trapped under there!

17:29.582 --> 17:32.650
That shell is what plunged
our city into darkness!

17:32.652 --> 17:35.253
Friends, we've got to get
the magical pink pearl...

17:35.255 --> 17:39.257
- [all] Captain Hook?
- A magical pearl, eh?

17:39.259 --> 17:41.325
Sounds like treasure!

17:41.327 --> 17:43.728
Treasure that doesn't
belong to you, Hook.

17:43.730 --> 17:47.298
We can't uncover it with
Hook standing on that shell!

17:47.300 --> 17:49.600
Bucky, can you
help us out?

17:53.572 --> 17:56.340
Quickly, Smee,
help me move this shell.

17:56.342 --> 18:00.678
- Put me down this instant!
- [Smee laughs] It tickles!

18:02.714 --> 18:04.749
- What in...
- Hang on, cap'n!

18:04.751 --> 18:07.718
We did it! We got rid of Hook.

18:07.720 --> 18:10.588
And we got two more
gold doubloons.

18:10.590 --> 18:13.791
Let's grab them
and go help Marina!

18:13.793 --> 18:17.261
How are we ever going
to lift this huge shell?

18:17.263 --> 18:20.364
It's as big as Bucky!
Even he can't lift it.

18:20.366 --> 18:23.768
I have an idea. Maybe some
of your friends can help?

18:23.770 --> 18:26.370
[gasping]
I bet they can!

18:26.372 --> 18:29.874
Friends of the deep,
whirl and swirl.

18:35.614 --> 18:38.683
- [Jake] Wow.
- [Cubby] Coconuts.

18:38.685 --> 18:41.853
[Izzy] It's beautiful.

18:48.694 --> 18:52.396
[gasps] Scaly tails!
What's this?

18:52.398 --> 18:57.335
[gasps] The anchor from
Captain Hook's <i>Jolly Roger</i>
<i>was inside the shell.</i>

18:57.337 --> 18:59.770
Hook's anchor must have hooked
the shell and pulled it,

18:59.772 --> 19:02.773
and the pink pearl,
out of Neptune's hand!

19:02.775 --> 19:05.643
Quickly, Smee!
Grab the pink pearl.

19:05.645 --> 19:08.412
It's time we take it
as our own!

19:08.414 --> 19:11.749
Oh, lookee, Captain!
Anchor ahoy!

19:11.751 --> 19:14.785
We found the treasure
and our missing anchor!

19:14.787 --> 19:17.321
That's two missions
accomplished.

19:17.323 --> 19:21.826
