going to stop me?

19:29.802 --> 19:31.836
[Jake] We are, Captain Hook!

19:31.838 --> 19:34.438
With the help of
Submarine Bucky.

19:35.807 --> 19:37.441
[both grunting]

19:39.411 --> 19:43.314
I shall not stop until
the pearl is mine!

19:43.316 --> 19:45.683
Um, cap'n, sir...

19:45.685 --> 19:49.687
[stuttering]
Sha-Sha-Sha-Sha...

19:49.689 --> 19:53.324
Oh. Shark!

19:53.326 --> 19:58.729
- Run, Smee, run!
- Running, sir, running!

19:58.731 --> 20:03.834
[chuckling] I don't think
we'll see old Feather Helmet
back down here anytime soon!

20:04.770 --> 20:08.339
[Jake] There.
Back where it belongs!

20:08.341 --> 20:09.840
- Wow.
- [Skully] Crackers.

20:09.842 --> 20:11.742
- [Cubby] Whoa.
- [Skully] So bright!

20:11.744 --> 20:13.477
[Izzy] Amazing!

20:13.479 --> 20:16.480
